==English==
===Noun phrase===
'''Los angelization''' (sometimes spelled "'''losangelization'''") is slang for disperse [[w:urban development]]; that is, [[urban sprawl]].
===Etymology===
"Los angelization" gets its name from the post-[[World War II]] growth of the '''City of [[Los Angeles]], [[California]]''' located in [[w:Southern California]] in the western [[United States]]. The city is the [[county seat]] of [[w:Los Angeles County, California|Los Angeles County]].

